itemDescription: British swimmer, Olympic athlete, Commonwealth Games bronze medallist

wikipedia_page.main: Malcolm Barrie Windeatt (born 5 April 1952) is a former British international swimmer who represented Great Britain at the 1972 Summer Olympics.
